hari</i> ‘army’. This was adopted by the Normans and introduced by them to England, superseding the native Old English form, <i>Wealdhere</i>. It was a very popular name in medieval England, normally pronounced ‘Water’."],"variants":[{"name":"Walther","meanings":["from <i>wald</i> ‘rule’ + <i>heri</i> ‘army’; name of the famous medieval minnesinger  Walther von der Vogelweide  (  <i>c.</i>1170– <i>c.</i>1230 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Sir Knight Walter Calverly was born on 1 January 1500, in Calverley, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter with Isabel Elizabeth Drakes. He died on 26 August 1547, in his hometown, at the age of 47."},"et":{"1 January 1500–26 August 1547":"1. jaanuar 1500–26. august 1547","1487–1540":"1487–1540","1509–1590":"1509–1590","1500–1547":"1500–1547","1547":"1547","1 January 1500":"1. jaanuar 1500","1500":"1500","1487":"1487","1540":"1540","1509":"1509","1590":"1590","26 August 1547":"26. august 1547","Calverley, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Calverley, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Scrooby, Nottinghamshire, England":"Scrooby, Nottinghamshire, England","Calverley, Yorkshire, England":"Calverley, Yorkshire, England"},"fi":{"1 January 1500–26 August 1547":"1. tammikuuta 1500–26. elokuuta 1547","1487–1540":"1487–1540","1509–1590":"1509–1590","1500–1547":"1500–1547","1547":"1547","1 January 1500":"1. tammikuuta 1500","1500":"1500","1487":"1487","1540":"1540","1509":"1509","1590":"1590","26 August 1547":"26. elokuuta 1547","Calverley, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Calverley, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Scrooby, Nottinghamshire, England":"Scrooby, Nottinghamshire, England","Calverley, Yorkshire, England":"Calverley, Yorkshire, England"},"fr":{"1 January 1500–26 August 1547":"1 janvier 1500–26 août 1547","1487–1540":"1487–1540","1509–1590":"1509–1590","1500–1547":"1500–1547","1547":"1547","1 January 1500":"1 janvier 1500","1500":"1500","1487":"1487","1540":"1540","1509":"1509","1590":"1